collections.name: Tarot League - Ancient Mythology Retold Through Graphic Illustrations
collections.description: Immerse yourself in a powerful visual narrative of contemporary graphic art that reveal the deepest truths about our human experience. This innovative tarot deck harnesses the vibrant energy of modern comic illustration and interprets the timeless lens of the tarot symbolism, generating a new visual language that is both a reflection of our times and a tribute to the classic legends that have inspired us for generations.

collections.name: Healing Tails
collections.description: Welcome to Healing Tails  – a heartwarming collection of anthropomorphic animals, each infused with charm, personality, and a touch of whimsy. My artwork brings adorable creatures to life, blending their natural beauty with human-like emotions and expressions. From serene foxes lost in thought to playful kittens sharing laughter, every piece is designed to bring comfort, warmth, and a sense of connection. Whether you're a collector or simply someone who appreciates the magic of art, I invite you to explore a world where animals and emotions intertwine in the most delightful way.

collections.name: Texas Moonlight
collections.description:
A warm summer night in Texas. The light of the moon shimmers on the water and the leaves of the live oak trees sway softly in the night breeze.  The song of cicadas fills the air. Coyotes yap in the distance.  The longhorns chew their cuds under the trees.  One lone steer lumbers to his feet and walks up on the riverbank. 

The night air is heavy and humid, but cooler than the breezes coming in from the fields that still carry the heat of the midday sun.  All the night things are awake and moving in the Texas Moonlight.  

Acrylic paintings by JJ Graber.
